short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Replace new tab page with a personal dashboard featuring currency converter and search

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Titan Mediaworks presents the Currency Converter - a finance oriented new tab homepage with currency converter and web search. It's the perfect way to start the day for business, finance, and accounting professionals or anyone who enjoys staying up to date on daily exchange rates.

By clicking "Add to Chrome"', you accept and agree to install the Chrome™ extension, set the Chrome™ New Tab to TX Currency Converter with web search by Bing, and to the Terms of Service and Privacy Policy.
